					</div>
					<div class="inline-block">
						<span class="peach-text big-text"><span class="border-bottom">goda</span> </span><br>
						<span class="peach-text">Weak<br>Adjective</span>
					</div>
					<div class="inline-block">
						<span class="red-text big-text"><span class="border-bottom">cyning</span> </span><br>
