					</div>
					<div class="inline-block">
						<span class="green-text big-text"><span class="border-bottom">onfeng</span> </span><br>
						<span class="green-text">Verb<br>&nbsp;</span>
					</div>
					<div class="inline-block">
						<span class="yellow-text big-text"><span class="border-bottom">him</span> </span><br>
						<span class="yellow-text">Object<br>Pronoun</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="padding-top">Most weak adjective endings are '<strong>an</strong>', but the masculine
